    • Constructor Detail

      • Snake

        public Snake​(double x,
             double y,
             Color c,
             double r,
             int l,
             int d)
        Constructs Snake object with x, y, diameter, color, radius, length, and direction specified by the respective parameters.
        Parameters:
        x - initial x position of head circle
        y - initial y position of head circle
        c - initial color of a snake's body
        r - initial radius of circles in a snake's body
        l - initial length of a snakes body in circles
        d - initial direction of a snake: EAST is 0, NORTH is 1, WEST is 2, SOUTH is 3
